remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObjectCollection.Add%2A> Metoda oczekuje tylko <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaExternal> i jego typów pochodnych (<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaImport>, <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaInclude>, i <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaRedefine>) jako parametry. Poniższy przykład przedstawia dodawanie dołączonego schematu do <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema.Includes%2A> kolekcji istniejącego <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> obiektu.  
  
```vb  
Dim schema As XmlSchema = New XmlSchema()  
  
Dim textReader As XmlTextReader = New XmlTextReader("include.xsd")  
Dim includeSchema As XmlSchema = XmlSchema.Read(textReader, null)  
  
Dim include As XmlSchemaInclude = New XmlSchemaInclude()  
include.Schema = includeSchema;  
schema.Includes.Add(include);  
```  
  
```csharp  
XmlSchema schema = new XmlSchema();  
  
XmlTextReader textReader = new XmlTextReader("include.xsd");  
XmlSchema includeSchema = XmlSchema.Read(textReader, null);  
  
XmlSchemaInclude include = new XmlSchemaInclude();  
include.Schema = includeSchema;  
schema.Includes.Add(include);  
```
